
'''Ruth Ama Gyan-Darkwa''' (wɔ woo no 29 May 2004) yɛ Ghanani nhomanimfo a oda nso. ɔyɛ  obi a osua koraa a w'anya akwanya sɛ adeusani wɔ suapɔn a ɛde Kwame Nkruma University of Science and Technology a ɛwɔ Kumasi <ref>My son will break his sister’s record – 13-year-old KNUST student’s father (ghanaweb.com)</ref><ref>KNUST admits 13-year-old prodigy - Graphic Online</ref><ref>13-year-old girl becomes one of Ghana's youngest university students | Africanews</ref><ref>13-year-old KNUST student says Akufo-Addo is her role model | Pulse Ghana</ref><ref>13 year old KNUST tells how she got to university at a young age - YEN.COM.GH</ref>.

== Ne mmɔfrase ne Nhomasua ==
Wɔ woo Gyan-Darkwa wɔ May da etɔ 29, afe 2004 mu wɔ Kumasi, a n'awofo ne Kwadwo Gyan-Darkwa ne ne hokafo. ɔhyee ne sukuu ase wɔ Christ Our Hope International School  a ewɔ Kumasi ne Abraham Lincoln Junior High School. Akyire, ɔtoaa so kɔɔ sukuu a ɛne Justice International school a  ɛwɔ Kumasi. Esiane ne sɛ na n'adwen mu dɔ yiyie nti, odi mmere kakra wɔ gyinae baako a, na w'abɔ no atra akɔ gyinae a edi na n'anim.  Bre a na w'adi mfie nkrɔn a na ogyina JSS1 wɔ Justice International School a ɛwɔ Kumasi no, ɔkyerɛw nsɔhwɛca ɛde Basic Educationa Certificate Examination maa no twaa nsɔhwe no. Eyi maa no nyaa akwanya sɛ adesuani wɔ ntoasoɔ  sukuu a ɛde St. Louis High School a ɛno nso wɔ Kumasi, na osuaa abɔdeɛ mu nyansapɛ a wɔfrɛ no science wɔ bre a na w'adi mfie du. Owiee ntoasoa sukuu wɔ afe 2017 wɔ bre a na wa'di mfie  dumienu. Wɔ afe 2017 mu no, wɔgyee no sɛ osuani wɔ Suapɔn a ɛde Kwame Nkruma University of Science and Technology maa no suaa Nkontabuo anaa Mathematics, eyi maa no beyɛɛ osuani a osua koraa a wagye no sɛ osuani wɔ Suapɔn no mu. 

Nea ɔyɛi yi ma ɔne n'abuasua nyaa sikafam mmoa firii Ghanafo w'agye din ahorɔw pii hɔ. Ghana manpanyin abediakyire yere a ne din de Samira Bawumia hyɛɛ bɔ sɛ ɔbɛfa ne ho ka nyinaa wɔ suapɔn no mu na afei nso, ɔbɛfa n'wofo ho ka a ɛfa ayeresa ho nyinaa. Ne nuabea a odi n'akyi a ode Josephine Gyan-Darkwa a otwaa ne nsɔhwɛ no nyaa mmoa firii Bernard Antwi Boasiko hɔ ma no kosuaa ne daeso a ɛne nnuruyɛ anaa nea pɔtɔ kasa mu  wɔfrɛ no medicine no wɔ Germany.

